<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Day 5: Unlock Advanced Features</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>‚ö° Day 5: Unlock Advanced Features</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hey <%= name %>,</h2>

            <p>Ready to level up? Here are the power features that separate content pros from the rest:</p>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>üé≠ Custom AI Personas</h3>
                <p>Train AI to write exactly like you. Define your voice, tone, and style once - use it forever.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>üí¨ AI Comment Generator</h3>
                <p>Engage with your network faster. Generate thoughtful comments that spark conversations.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>üìä Profile Analyzer</h3>
                <p>Get AI-powered insights on any LinkedIn profile. Perfect for networking and partnerships.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>ü™ù Viral Hook Library</h3>
                <p>Access 1000+ proven hooks. Start every post with maximum impact.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL || 'http://localhost:3000' %>/dashboard" class="cta-button">
                    Explore All Features ‚Üí
                </a>
            </div>

            <div
                style="background-color: #e3f2fd; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
                <strong style="color: #1565c0;">üíé Power User Tip:</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #1565c0;">Create 3-5 different personas for different content types
                    (thought leadership, storytelling, educational). This gives you variety without losing authenticity.
                </p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>What's next?</strong><br>
                In 2 days, we'll send your weekly success report with personalized recommendations!</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">You're doing amazing!<br><strong>The LinkedInPulse Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> LinkedInPulse. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>